nodes.text:
This starship was owned by Dezono Qua and operated by his astromech droid,
known as H2. In 19 BBY, former Jedi Dass Jennir killed Qua and took the ship,
as well as H2, for himself. He used it to travel to Cato Neimoidia and, later, Telerath.
On the way to Vondarc, it was damaged in a dogfight with two Alpha-3 Nimbus-class V-wing starfighters over the planet Prine and crashed.
